rows.label: qev085807_MSG0001
rows.name:
We need you to take down the chasm forfexes
holed up in the canyon here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085807_MSG0002
rows.name:
Once they're out of the picture, we can install that data
probe in a jiffy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085807_MSG0003
rows.name:
So get in there and knock 'em dead for us!
...Er, literally.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085807_MSG0004
rows.name:
Does this mean those indigens have been cleared out?
Ha! The legend of Team Elma lives on![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085807_MSG0005
rows.name:
Through the canyon there's a hill with a great view of
the sea. We'll head in just as soon as we're ready,
but why don't you go ahead and meet us there?[ST:wait ]
